            <ul>
                <li>Monday-Friday: 06.00 - 23.00</li>
                <li>Saturday-Sunday: 08.00 - 20.00</li>
                <li>Emergency Room: 24/7</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-tile-2 grid-width">
        <img src="/calendar.svg" class="grid_icons">
            <p>Book you appointment:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>You are able to book your appointment with
                your doctor under the appointments menu..</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-tile-3 grid-width">
        <img src="/ambulance.svg" class="grid_icons">
            <p>Is there an emergency?</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Tel.: +1 FLATIRON-ER-0101</li>
                <li>Call the number and our ER time
                will come to you!</li>
            </ul>
